author: JuliaRegistrator

comments.body:
Dear @KristofferC, 
I am sorry to ping you directly, but you merged FEMMaterials.jl v0.1.0. @thelfer organizes the next MFront User Meeting on the 17th of October (in five days), and it would be really cool if he could announce our first release of MFrontInterface.jl. Thank you in advance.

I've created release `v0.1.0`, [here](https://github.com/JuliaFEM/MFrontInterface.jl/releases/tag/v0.1.0) it is.
<!-- a4307f50-f05c-11e9-8e7f-3d58de33e750 -->
